These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: coffee, fanta
Color: blue, fuchsia
Hobby: photography, card-games
Job: engineer, analyst
1. Job:analyst is on the left or right of Hobby:card-games##3
2. Beverage:fanta is in an even position##4
3. Color:fuchsia == Beverage:coffee##1
4. Job:analyst is on the right of Job:engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Color   | fuchsia     | blue   |
| Hobby         | card-games | photography |
| Job     | engineer | analyst    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Nationality: malaysian, nigerian
Color: blood-red, grey
Pet: dog, rat
House: victorian, townhouse
1. Pet:rat is in an odd position##4
2. Color:blood-red == House:townhouse##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Color:grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | malaysian     | nigerian |
| Color   | grey | blood-red  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| House     | victorian   | townhouse    |

 #################################
 
