.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
City: berlin, edinburgh
Beverage: tea, coffee
Food: peach, potato
Sport: climbing, soccer
1. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
2. Beverage:coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. City:edinburgh == Beverage:tea##1
4. Food:peach is on the left of Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| City           | edinburgh | berlin    |
| Beverage   | tea       | coffee |
| Food           | peach         | potato    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

